Class BilancialTableModel

java.lang.Object
  fs.fibu2.view.model.BilancialTableModel
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.util.EventListener, javax.swing.event.TreeExpansionListener, javax.swing.event.TreeModelListener, javax.swing.table.TableModel
public class BilancialTableModel
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.swing.table.TableModel, javax.swing.event.TreeExpansionListener, javax.swing.event.TreeModelListener

This model contains the bilancial valued obtained from a BilancialTree. It does not save any values, but gets them from the tree's model. It also listens to the expansion state of the tree and displays only rows for visible tree rows

Author:
Simon Hampe
